tafsir[13]{c,v,t}:
  19,39,"Hul…ďinir -an Nulaa…óo- yim…ďe …ďen √Ďalnde Nimse tuma nimsata bonnu…óo on e hoore bonnere makko nden, mo∆ī∆īin…óo on kadi [nimsa] anngal hibbingol makko …óoftaare nden, tuma nde …óeri dewal ngal taggaa, hasboore ma…ď…ďe nden timmi, gooto kala hikkondiri e ko o ardinnoo kon, hari kam…ďe ka ngurndam ma…ď…ďe aduna ko …ďe hoditor…ďe …óam, ko …ďe welsindii…ďe fii Laakara, toode kam…ďe …ďe gom…óinaano √Ďalnde Darngal."
  19,40,"Menen, ko Menen woni heddotoo…ďe …ďen …ďaawo re'ugol tagoore nden, Men rona leydi ndin, Men ronira kadi …ďen wonu…ďe e hoore mayri re'ugol …ďe e heddagol Amen …ďaawo ma…ď…ďe, e Jeyal Amen e ma…ď…ďe, e firlitorgol Amen e ma…ď…ďe no Men Yi…óiri, ko ka Amen Menen Tun …ďe ruttoytee √Ďalnde Darngal fii Hasboore e Njo…ďdi."
  19,41,"JaŇčto -an Nulaa…óo- ka Alqur'aanaare Tellinaande e maa…óa kumpital fii Ibraahiima (yo o his), pellet, konko o laatino heewu…óo Goonga e Goonginngol Aayeeje Alla …óen, ko o Annabaajo kadi immorde ka Alla."
  19,42,"Tuma nde o maakannoo baaba makko Aajara: "Ko an yo baaba; ko hon…óun rewantaa gaanin Alla sanamuuru ndu nanataa noddaandu maa…óa ndun si a noddii ndu, ndu yi'ataa dewal maa…óa ngal si a rewii ndu, ndu ittantaa ma lorra, ndu poo…óantaa ma nafa."
  19,43,"Ko an yo baaba, min dey gom…óii arii e am immorde e Ganndal e laawol wahayu ko araali e maa…óa, jokkam mi fewne e Laawol Focciingol."
  19,44,"Ko an yo baaba, wata a …óofto Seytaane rewaa mo, pellet, Seytaane laatike yeddu…óo Hinnorante, nokku ka O Yamirnoo mo sujjanngol Aadama o sujjaali."
  19,45,"Ko an yo baaba, min dey mi…óo huli wata Lepte he…ďe immorde ka Hinnorante si a maayii e hoore keeferaaku maa ngun, laato…óaa …ďadii…óo Seytaane ka Lepte sabu weldigal maa…óa e makko."
  19,46,"Aajara wi'ani …ďi…ó…óo makko on Ibraahiima (yo o his): "Enee, an Ibraahiima a …óuuroto …óii sanamuuji am …ói mi rawata?! pellet, si a tertaaki yennugol sanamji am …óin mi fi…óirte kaa∆īe, seedu e am jamaanu juu-tungu wata a yewtam, wata a wonndu e am."
  19,47,"Ibraahiima (yo o his) maaki: "Kisiyee e maa…óa immorde e am, a he…ďataa ko mettaymaa ko iwri e am, mi toranto ma haforaneede e peewal ka Joomi am, pellet, Kanko O Senike ko O heewu…óo Newanaade lam."
  19,48,"Mi seeda e mo'on mi seeda kadi e …óin rewetee…ói mon …ói rewoton …óum gaanin Alla. Mi toroo Joomi am Kanko Tun mi kafidataa Mo e huunde, no gasa O salantaako lam si mi torike Mo, mi laatoo malkisaa…óo sabu toragol Mo."
  19,49,"Tuma nde o accidunoo…ďe e reweetee…ói ma…ď…ďe …ói …ďe woni rewude …óin gaanin Alla, Men lontinani mo e hattagol yim…ďe makko …ďen Men Okki mo …ďi…ó…óo makko on Ishaaqa, Men Okki mo taniraawo makko on Yaaquuba, Men wa…ói gooto kala e ma…ď…ďe Annabaajo."
  19,50,"Men Okki …ďe e Yurmeende Amen wonndude e Annabaaku ngun mo∆ī∆īere …óuu…óunde, Men wa…óani …ďe mantoore mo∆ī∆īere jokkondirnde e …óen…óe jeyaa…ďe …ďen."
  19,51,"JaŇčto -an Nulaa…óo- ka Alqur'aanaare Tellinaande e maa…óa kabaaru fii Muusaa (yo o his), kanko o woniino Su…ďaa…óo Siiwaa, o woniino kadi Nulaa…óo Annabaajo."